Overview

This dashboard shows Decryption overview related to the Prisma Access Integration.

The dashboard is made to provide general statistics and show the ingested Decryption logs from Prisma Access.

It provides detailed insights into decryption events critical to our network security. It categorizes decryption events by chain status and proxy type, offering clarity on how data is processed and secured. The dashboard highlights the top 10 errors encountered, along with the source and destination addresses with the highest number of failed connections, aiding in troubleshooting and incident response. Additionally, decryption events are analyzed by key exchange algorithm, encryption algorithm, and hash algorithm, providing essential details.
